body.description: Add a cheerful and inviting look to your living space with the Superior Medallion Indoor Area Rug. Made from durable materials, this rug is incredibly sturdy while remaining soft and comfortable underfoot. Displaying large oversized medallions over a beautiful foundation, this rug is available in a variety of color options to match your decor. The cozy pile height is plush and easy to maintain, making this rug a long-lasting option for homes with children and pets.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Why Superior? We created Superior products with the purpose of filling your life with long-lasting luxury. Our company has grown into an affordable home luxury brand specializing in area rugs, bedding, bath linens, and curtains. All products are made with premium materials that have been designed to bring you a consistently exceptional experience. We pride ourselves on a commitment to tradition with our fabrics and textiles. SUPERIOR ELEGANT MEDALLION AREA RUG COLLECTION Durable, long-lasting flooring Displaying a hint of old-world charm, create the space you always wanted with the timeless design of the elegant floral medallion and blossom-filled accents. MULTIPLE COLOR OPTIONS: 3 Colors (Coffee, Midnight blue, Toffee) The beautifully designed Crawford rug adds an elegant touch of style with its graciousness that will complement any room in your home. This rug collection has the beauty and suppleness of a traditional pile that is altogether practical, durable, and colorful. The elegant floral medallion motif gives your room classic style This area rug will look great in your living room, kitchen, or basement

Complete the Look of Any Room REFRESH ANY ROOM FROM THE GROUND UP This classic design boasts a blooming floral medallion with border of budding florals flourishing between lovely scrolled vines. CREATE A COZY FOUNDATION This family-friendly rug is crafted from Polypropylene with a long-lasting jute backing to handle your most frequented areas of your home. HARDWORKING & VERSATILE Ideal for homes with children and pets, this rug can resist common spills and stains making it perfect for everyday use. CLASSIC SILHOUETTE PAIRS WITH ANY DECOR Available in your choice of three neutral colorways, this lovely piece is sure to coordinate effortlessly with your existing décor.

How to Choose the Right Size Area Rug Runner Rug Size: 2'7"x 8' and 2'x11' Recommended Room: Hallway, Entryway, Bedroom Pro tip: Runners are the perfect way to dress up any hallway in your home or decorate any narrow space that could use a cozier foundation. Small Scatter Rugs Size: 2'x3' and 3'x5' Recommended Room: Entryway, Kitchen, Bathroom, Laundry Room, Playroom Pro tip: This versatile rectangular size works great in front of doorways and can also work as a small landing space when you need a little extra padding. Medium-Size Rugs: 4'x6', 5'x8' and 6'x9' Recommended Room: Living Room, Bedroom, Playroom, Dining Room Pro tip: Perfect for smaller living spaces, it's easy to define a specific seating area with a medium-size rug. Large-Size Area Rugs: 8'x10' and 9'x12' Recommended Room: Bedroom, Living Room, Dining Rooms, Nursery Pro tip: Create a central focus to any medium or large living area that provides a soft cushion underfoot while also framing your space.

reviews.reviewText: I really love this rug but it is not blue of any shade. It says midnight blue but is most definitely a coffee color. I will keep this rug but still want the correct color rug for my main room.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A great bargain
reviews.reviewText: This was such a steal! It's been only two days and the edges and corners have almost completely flattened out without any rug pad or grippers. Does not slide at all and feels soft under the feet. The colour combination is vibrant and livens up our living room. It did have a strong smell when we unpacked it but that's gone now. I'm very happy with my choice!
